Travel and Expense Reimbursement Policy
 This document outlines the policy for reimbursing employees for business-related expenses.
 Eligible Expenses:- Flights, hotels, meals, and ground transportation.- Client entertainment with prior manager approval.
 Submission Process:- All receipts must be uploaded via the Expense Portal within 14 days of the trip.- Reimbursements are processed within 7 business days.
